- Window: **60 seconds**
- Implemented in Supabase Edge Functions

### Audit Logging (Already Enabled):
- All admin operations logged ✅
- Referral events tracked ✅
- Payment operations audited ✅

## Monitoring & Alerts

### Sentry Alerts:
- Errors: Immediate notification
- Rate limit threshold warnings
- Payment processing errors
- Referral system failures

### Database Monitoring:
- Query performance via pg_stat_statements
- Connection pool utilization
- Replication lag (if applicable)

### Uptime Monitoring:
- Ping monitoring: https://uptimerobot.com (recommended)
- Health check endpoint: `/api/health` (optional to create)

## Performance Baselines

### Expected Metrics (from Phase 4 optimization):
- Page load time: < 2s
- API response time: < 500ms
- Checkout completion: < 3s
- Rate limit triggers: < 0.1% of requests

### Indexing Impact:
- Referral code lookups: ~5ms (down from ~50ms)
- Referral use queries: ~3ms (down from ~30ms)
- Audit log queries: ~10ms (down from ~100ms)

## Rollback Procedure

If issues occur in production:

```bash
# Revert to previous build in Vercel:
1. Go to Vercel Dashboard → Deployments
2. Click "Redeploy" on last successful build
3. Or use: git revert HEAD && git push

# Revert migrations (if needed):
supabase db push --no-new-migration  # or manually drop indexes
```

## Post-Deployment Verification

Run these checks:
- [ ] Homepage loads without errors
- [ ] Login flow works
- [ ] Checkout form appears
- [ ] Referral code input visible
- [ ] Points display correct tier
- [ ] Admin dashboard accessible
- [ ] Sentry receiving events
- [ ] Rate limiting works (test with 11 requests in 1min)
- [ ] Audit logs appear in admin panel
